QuestData.Title: Hungry Pups
QuestData.Description: Ah, a new arrival! Good that you're here $g lad:lass;! The pups are hungry and we're completely out of food.$B$BThankfully they love dragon meat, which fortuitously exists in abundance within the Charred Vale, south of here.$B$BBe a good $g boy:girl; and fetch me several pounds of black dragon whelp filet.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent. The dogs will be well fed and ready to defend our outpost for weeks!
